ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectNo. 137 - (Manitoba) Provincial Emergencies Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER N° 137 - which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of MANITOBA with respect to the FLOODING that affected the region as a result of the 2011 spring breakup.
